name: Neon - Maze 004
description:
The 4th artwork follows a semi-chaotic style, blending mandala-type concentric evolution drawing with random inner patterns when you can see fine branches flowing from thick veins. The background color comes from my almost empty coffee mug, waiting for another dosage to finish the day in a good way. On the other hand, the foreground color is a clean greenish-bluish tone, bringing some light from stars which I can see from my windows just now.

🖌️✍🏼♒

1200x1200
Drawn within: 4h43min
